Delete a poll and all its votes. QUERY matches the poll in polls by PARAM.poll_id and bulk-deletes via DELETE PRIMARY RECORDNUMBERS; OPEN+DELETE removes the matching votes by the same key. Outputs STATUS|OK + VOTES_DELETED|N on success, or STATUS|NOT_FOUND when no poll matches. Accepts PARAM.poll_id. Used by the results page "Delete Poll" button (published with an action token for write authorization).
